node.text: FINALLY!!! Y’all know we had a ton of p.o packages stacking up and I finally got around to opening them! There’s 3 parts so stay tuned to the others 😘

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by De'arra Taylor on September 03, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, child and people standing.

node.text:
Dear Grandaddy,

as we laid you to rest today I want you to know since the day I took my first breath on this earth you where there every step of the way. you have been by my side always and was there anytime I needed you. you’ve taught me how to love, how to care, how to drive and even how to cook. you showed up to every event and every special moment in my life. you were my father figure, the man I ran to about anything, the main guy in my life was you grandaddy and will forever be you. you spoiled me, you gave me everything I ever wanted and needed. there’s so many first I’ve experienced with you like road tripping around the country, my first camera, my first MacBook, eating pig feet and the list goes on. I appreciate you and I love you forever to the moon and back. you’re my everything. thank you for the best 25 years of my life. I’ll miss you always

Love, your DeeDee ❤️
